{"tid":1440971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分散式系統] 主導這場運動是蜂群思维","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T01:36:48.000Z","uid":31320,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4cce43227a363138979e49a631e60962495ffc","tid":1440971,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"作為&ldquo;超級有機體&rdquo;的蜂群，被稱為&ldquo;分散式系統&rdquo;，是以生物邏輯建立起來的群集模型。它依靠成千上萬個發條一起驅動的一個並行的系統，來進行生產，進行自維持。它有四個突出特點，活系統的特質正是由此而來：<br />\n<br />\n　　（1）沒有強制性的中心控制；<br />\n<br />\n　　（2）次級單位具有自治的特質；<br />\n<br />\n　　（3）次級單位之間彼此高度連接；<br />\n<br />\n　　（4）點對點間的影響通過網路形成了非線性因果關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.mbalib.com/zh-tw/蜂巢思维\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.mbalib.com%2Fzh-tw%2F%E8%9C%82%E5%B7%A2%E6%80%9D%E7%BB%B4&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=861951c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.mbalib.com/zh-tw/蜂巢思维</a><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦，老董，689，柒婆，葉國謙，葉劉<br />\n找大台找幕後黑手吧！<br />\n<br />\n不過點解釋你地班廢老都唔會明架喇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362c39b3dd82be874055c900402fa8bcae3041d4","tid":1440971,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e334b15a761f2deda0148acc25662a466d24dc6","tid":1440971,"uid":276514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"We are the swarm("},{"pid":"15e041110954bef9a18f49876811690f947885a0","tid":1440971,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4fe42700f5a4f57f259f99fae4724d9245f234","tid":1440971,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d428c8356cd5b5